# Backing store for the fETH internal wallet / off-chain Predict markets
# (src/lib/offchainWallet.ts). Required before deploying to Vercel (or any
# serverless host) — without these, fETH state is written to a local JSON
# file that does NOT persist across serverless invocations.
#
# Get these from an Upstash Redis database: create one at
# https://console.upstash.com (or add the Upstash integration from the
# Vercel Marketplace when setting up this project on Vercel), then copy its
# REST URL and token here / into your Vercel project's env vars.
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
